text: Westerhout 49 also known as W49, is a strong galactic thermal radio source. It is studied by astronomers. It seems to be part of an HII region. It was discovered by Gart Westerhout in 1958. ==Related pages== *Aquila (constellation) *List of most luminous stars *Westerhout 49-2 ==Other websites== * Category:Astronomy
